Purpose

This document defines the cognitive operating model of Numera.

Rather than describing software components, this document explains how Numera transforms information into decisions.

Every AI capability, backend service, workflow and user interaction must align with this model.

This document is the conceptual foundation of the Numera Brain.

⸻

Core Philosophy

Numera does not automate because it can.

Numera automates because it understands.

Automation is the consequence of understanding.

Not the objective.

⸻

Cognitive Mission

Numera exists to continuously transform business information into trusted financial decisions.

To achieve this, Numera must:

* perceive information;
* understand meaning;
* connect knowledge;
* remember experience;
* reason using context;
* evaluate confidence;
* plan actions;
* execute safely;
* reflect on outcomes;
* improve continuously.

⸻

The Cognitive Loop

Every interaction follows the same reasoning cycle.

Perception
      ↓
